{"tid":2055823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"跳閘被捉惹爭執 維修員被指連摑港鐵職員八巴掌 職員作供時形容被告老豆教仔咁","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T09:42:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a63623dbedccdbd56d87469e7d7e1a3615ecf9","tid":2055823,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200608/FL2D6GH7Z24NSM6WYVPSLH42HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200608%2FFL2D6GH7Z24NSM6WYVPSLH42HY%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f0d1fe1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200608%2FFL2D6GH7Z24NSM6WYVPSLH42HY%2F&h=0d1673e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200608/FL2D6GH7Z24NSM6WYVPSLH42HY/</a><br />\n<br />\n樂器維修員去年10月14日疑因跳閘而與港鐵職員爭執，其間維修員被指連摑港鐵職員八巴掌，被控普通襲擊罪，案件今開審。職員作供時形容被告掌摑的力度猶如「老豆教仔咁，唔係好重手」。辯方則指當日職員揚言「依家出嚟打鑊你」，更向被告揮動對講機，被告是為擋職員繼續逼近，才將雙手放在職員面頰，根本沒有襲擊及掌摑職員。"},{"pid":"7b0e388715054de397a509581bc4ce8417a07ffb","tid":2055823,"uid":331739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"哇屌 呢個直頭要頒大紫荊勳章比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爽"},{"pid":"c7233295ae59e3f0ca6106668cbf6782a72e9cca","tid":2055823,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"直接大巴大巴車埋去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7141e8980b955e7582e36eb8eb6f612c614387","tid":2055823,"uid":272010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"點解狗鐵職猿都幫個手足講好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d71e17957cce732f1708a9615217927a3639